title: Best of Watercolor-Painting Light and Shadow (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Best of Watercolor: Painting Light & Shadow

Rockport Publishers | 1997 | ISBN: 1564963489 | English | 150 pages | PDF | 17.8 MB


Explore the possibilities! Painting Light and Shadow presents an unlimited range of creative watercolor art. Selected from over four thousand entries, the featured artists were chosen for their outstanding talent in portraying light and shadow in their work. This collection includes: More than 130 paintings in a multitude of styles and techniques by artists from many different countries
